      title: Write docs/SELF_MODIFYING_GUIDE.md
      status: todo
      description: 'Create a guide covering: (1) Canvas STORE pattern -- how to write text to canvas cells, (2) ASMSELF + RUNNEXT pattern -- compile and execute, (3) Register passing -- sharing state between
        generations, (4) Self-reading -- using LOAD from canvas to inspect your own source, (5) Pitfalls -- infinite loops, corruption, error handling. Include code snippets for each pattern.

        '
      dependencies:
      - p48.d1.t1
      acceptance_criteria:
